net.sf.jclec

Interface IIndividual

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JCLEC, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIndividual, BinArrayIndividual, ExprTreeIndividual, IntArrayIndividual, MultiExprTreeIndividual, MultiSyntaxTreeIndividual, RealArrayIndividual, SyntaxTreeIndividual

    public interface IIndividual
extends JCLEC
    General purpose individual. This interface defines common operations for a general-purpose individual. Methods implementation depends on the individual's encoding -that is, what is the type of genotype it presents, the presence of phenotype, ...

    Author:
    Sebastian Ventura
